    "causal_summary": "The mcp-code-mode stdio MCP server (`mcp_server/index.ts`) connected its transport and never handled session end: no stdin-EOF handler, no transport-close handler, no parent watchdog. A hard-killed parent session left the process alive, reparented to PID 1, permanently. Sixteen such orphans (up to 11 days old) had accumulated and degraded shared daemon infrastructure, contributing to bridge-probe timeouts in new sessions.",
